        <h1 class="rr-title">Database Census Report</h1>
        <p class="rr-pitch">Generated locally by the open-source CLI. hoop.dev brings governed access to every one of these databases &mdash; for humans and AI agents. <a href="https://hoop.dev" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer" class="rr-pitch-link">Get to know hoop.dev &rarr;</a></p>
        <div class="rr-meta-row">
          <span class="rr-meta-chip" id="chip-scope"></span>
